{"tid":2010786,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"鄺俊宇公職不獲續任 學者：政府敵我分明","createTime":"2020-05-10T15:31:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T16:08:07.000Z","uid":149978,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1aa9528d21ef6bd4ea769f7cce909338c64debb5","tid":2010786,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T15:31:14.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】繼法律界立法會議員郭榮鏗早前不獲政府續任競委會委員後，政府昨公布新一屆公共圖書館諮詢委員會任命，當中民主黨鄺俊宇由2016年起出任委員，在新名單中未有上榜，同樣未達政府公職可擔任6年的限期。鄺俊宇表示，政府並未聯絡他談續任事宜。<br />\n<br />\n委員會職能包括就公共圖書館的發展向政府提供意見，如圖書館設施及服務的發展策略、措施，及與各界合作推廣閱讀風氣等。現任主席為城大副校長李惠光，新獲委任的委員包括民建聯鄭泳舜、環境局前政治助理蔡少綿等7人。除了鄺俊宇外，金管局助理總裁（機構拓展及營運）蘇家碧亦在2016年起任委員、今次未有再上榜。<br />\n<br />\n鄺俊宇回應本報查詢時表示，政府並未聯絡他談續任，但認為此公職權責相對較輕，對未獲續任「沒什麼特別感覺」，目前集中工作較繁重的扶貧委員會。他相信過去數年於諮詢委員會所給予的意見都足夠，至於是否針對民主派，鄺俊宇稱「要問番政府」，但認為性質與郭榮鏗未獲續任競委會不同，因競委會權責較大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200508/s00002/1588876939153/%E9%84%BA%E4%BF%8A%E5%AE%87%E5%85%AC%E8%81%B7%E4%B8%8D%E7%8D%B2%E7%BA%8C%E4%BB%BB-%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%95%B5%E6%88%91%E5%88%86%E6%98%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200508%2Fs00002%2F1588876939153%2F%25E9%2584%25BA%25E4%25BF%258A%25E5%25AE%2587%25E5%2585%25AC%25E8%2581%25B7%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%258D%25B2%25E7%25BA%258C%25E4%25BB%25BB-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%2580%2585-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2595%25B5%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%2598%258E&d=18ndJK2uCT0lbSM6MbdNQswCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=dfa4f52b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200508%2Fs00002%2F1588876939153%2F%25E9%2584%25BA%25E4%25BF%258A%25E5%25AE%2587%25E5%2585%25AC%25E8%2581%25B7%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%258D%25B2%25E7%25BA%258C%25E4%25BB%25BB-%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%2580%2585-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2595%25B5%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%2598%258E&h=96851ab2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200508/s00002/1588876939153/%E9%84%BA%E4%BF%8A%E5%AE%87%E5%85%AC%E8%81%B7%E4%B8%8D%E7%8D%B2%E7%BA%8C%E4%BB%BB-%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%95%B5%E6%88%91%E5%88%86%E6%98%8E</a>"},{"pid":"e4fad647f9d3ce1c894f9199f8e0c4fce3ccabae","tid":2010786,"uid":21319,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T15:33:31.000Z","msg":"用人唯親"},{"pid":"0d97076c41f3674c2d4a31af2ca2b21e1efeba23","tid":2010786,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T15:35:36.000Z","msg":"又搵鄧炳強做"},{"pid":"57edf8406e8b3ddf81b8e3d47f51774439f017ac","tid":2010786,"uid":271516,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T15:46:35.000Z","msg":"搵落選果班做？"},{"pid":"1c04e5b060623e4c0eb64cf841c67a0ef9e06ce4","tid":2010786,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T15:50:35.000Z","msg":"唔怪得知d古典文學咁難搵，希望唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f6323f5e78d5ea0e623a0a1a9dc74c680a8b5b","tid":2010786,"uid":321854,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T16:04:43.000Z","msg":"公共圖書館有實體五毛大家可以諗諗點樣接佢地收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af638643f4707846a8cbd98ed5d5caba515761bd","tid":2010786,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0d97076c41f3674c2d4a31af2ca2b21e1efeba23","tid":2010786,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T15:35:36.000Z","msg":"又搵鄧炳強做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T16:05:03.000Z","msg":"清風不識字，唔會點讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d53bce634cab3fb77a